      "position": [
        -80,
        1152
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 512,
        "height": 128,
        "content": "## B. Sticky: “Message type detection”\n\nThis step detects whether the incoming Telegram message is text or voice and routes the workflow accordingly."
