        1328
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 400,
        "height": 272,
        "content": "## C. Sticky: “AI personal assistant agent”\n\nThis is the core AI agent. It uses an OpenAI chat model, short-term memory, and multiple tools to understand user requests and execute actions such as sending emails, managing contacts, scheduling events, performing research, or running calculations.\n\nThe assistant follows predefined rules to ensure safe, consistent, and professional behavior."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
